### 1. 发布测试消息（等价于你的 curl）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test-publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "test/topic",
  "payload": "{\"message\":\"hello\"}"
}

### 2. 再发一条别的消息（可选）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/test-publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "demo/alert",
  "payload": "{\"temp\":42,\"unit\":\"°C\"}"
}